Excellent! Now I have all the information I need. Let me provide a comprehensive report of my findings.

## Freedom Wall Feature Investigation Report

I've thoroughly investigated the Freedom Wall feature, including the sticker system and stamp functionality. Here's a complete breakdown:

### 1. STICKER SYSTEM

